Package: nptui
Version: 1.0.1
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: NPTUI Developer <dev@example.com>
Description: Netplan TUI - Terminal User Interface for Netplan
 A terminal-based user interface for managing network configuration
 using netplan. Similar to nmtui but designed specifically for netplan.
 .
 Features:
  - Configure network interfaces
  - Set IP addresses (DHCP or Static)
  - Configure DNS servers
  - Manage network settings easily
Depends: netplan.io

